import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"xyz-ui"}}>{`Xyz UI`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`打造属于自己的组件库 ⛹⛹`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="img" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"src":"https://blogaaaaxzh.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/LogoPng.png","alt":"Xyz-Ui"}}></MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"component"}}>{`Component`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul" props={{"className":"task-list-item"}}><MDXTag name="input" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"type":"checkbox","checked":true,"disabled":true}}></MDXTag>{` `}{`typography`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul" props={{"className":"task-list-item"}}><MDXTag name="input" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"type":"checkbox","checked":true,"disabled":true}}></MDXTag>{` `}{`box`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"tools"}}>{`Tools`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul" props={{"className":"task-list-item"}}><MDXTag name="input" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"type":"checkbox","checked":true,"disabled":true}}></MDXTag>{` `}{`xyz-cli`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
